        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Requirement</strong> Your previous action was to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.Unleash Psyche]{Unleash your Psyche}.</p><hr /><p>The force of your mind unleashing itself wracks your enemies with a violent shockwave that batters your enemies. You deal @Damage[ceil(@actor.level/2)d6[force]|options:area-damage] damage to all creatures in a @Template[emanation|distance:20], with a @Check[reflex|against:occult|basic|options:area-effect] save.</p>\n<p>At 5th level and every 2 levels thereafter, the damage increases by 1d6.</p>"
